OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F407A1772910673
OL,3,CSchool children want kits to treat
OL,4,Cstab wounds to be put in bus stations
OL,6,FSchool children in London are now so
OL,7,Fconcerned for their safety, they are
OL,8,Furging transport bosses to put medical
OL,9,Fkits to treat stab victims in bus
OL,10,Fstations.
OL,12,FThe call for the bleed kits has come
OL,13,Ffrom teenage members of the London
OL,14,FYouth Assembly, they're at City Hall
OL,15,Ftoday working with members of the
OL,16,Fauthority who want to push the motion
OL,17,Fthrough.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G1/5
