OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F407A1772910673
OL,3,CSchool children want kits to treat
OL,4,Cstab wounds to be put in bus stations
OL,6,FIt comes after Kelyan Bokassa, a 14-
OL,7,Fyear-old from south London was stabbed
OL,8,Fto death on a bus in Woolwich last
OL,9,Fyear.
OL,11,FBleed kits are designed to manage
OL,12,Fcatastrophic bleeding. Unlike standard
OL,13,Ffirst aid kits, which are made for
OL,14,Fminor injuries, bleed kits contain
OL,15,Fspecialist equipment to treat life-
OL,16,Fthreatening blood loss.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/5
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
