PN,40703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F407A1772910673
OL,3,CSchool children want kits to treat
OL,4,Cstab wounds to be put in bus stations
OL,6,FThe kits are used to slow or stop
OL,7,Fbleeding following a serious injury.
OL,8,FThey support responders in controlling
OL,9,Fblood loss from wounds that could
OL,10,Fotherwise prove fatal before EMS reach
OL,11,Fthe scene.
OL,13,FThe London Assembly notes that:
OL,15,F Catastrophic bleeding can result in
OL,16,Fdeath within minutes, and immediate
OL,17,Fintervention is often the determining
OL,18,Ffactor in survival.
OL,26,@wD@Abf
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/5
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
