OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,408,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F407A1772910673
OL,3,CSchool children want kits to treat
OL,4,Cstab wounds to be put in bus stations
OL,6,FThe Assembly is calling on Transport
OL,7,Ffor London to work with the London
OL,8,FAmbulance Service to put publicly
OL,9,Faccessible kits in all major bus
OL,10,Fstations.
OL,12,FIt wants areas with the highest levels
OL,13,Fof serious violence to be prioritised
OL,14,Ffor the roll out.
OL,16,FIt is also calling for first aid
OL,17,Ftraining for bus drivers and frontline
OL,18,Fstaff, to ensure confidence in
OL,19,Fresponding to catastrophic bleeding
OL,20,Femergencies.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G5/5
